    "en": {
      "title": "The fuel queue takes another toll",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "A person waiting in the queue to get petrol at Payagala IOC petrol station has died early this morning.",
        "It is said that the deceased was a driver of a mobile ice cream van belonging to a private company (Elephant House).",
        "The police said that he was a 60-year-old man named Hilary Fernando, who was a resident of Moratuwa Rawatawatta area.",
        "He had been waiting in the queue for three days and suddenly fell ill in the queue at around 1.30 this morning."
      ],
